'''Recuva'''是一個由[[Piriform|Piriform]]開發的[[免費軟件|免費]][[數據恢復|數據恢復]]軟件，能夠在Microsoft Windows執行。該軟體能夠恢復被「永久」刪除以及被作業系統標示為可用空間的檔案。此外，亦能夠恢復在[[快閃裝置|快閃裝置]]、[[記憶卡|記憶卡]]或[[MP3播放器|MP3播放器]]中被刪除的檔案<ref>{{cite web|url=https://softonline.net/recuva-for-windows|title=Recuva  - free  file recovery software|work=Softonline.net|accessdate=2020-09-09|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917003030/https://softonline.net/recuva-for-windows/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.technibble.com/repair-tool-of-the-week-recuva-portable/|title=Repair  Tool of the Week: Recuva Portable|work=technibble.com|accessdate=2009-01-01|archive-date=2017-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171210175703/https://www.technibble.com/repair-tool-of-the-week-recuva-portable/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。支援的[[檔案系統|檔案系統]]有[[FAT12|FAT12]]、[[FAT16|FAT16]]、[[FAT32|FAT32]]、[[exFAT|exFAT]]、[[NTFS|NTFS]]、[[NTFS5|NTFS5]]、[[NTFS|NTFS]]、[[EFS|EFS]]、[[ext2|ext2]]、[[ext3|ext3]]、[[ext4|ext4]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.filehippo.com/download_recuva/60713|title=Recuva 1.52.1086|work=FileHippo|accessdate=2015-04-08|archive-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416221006/http://filehippo.com/download_recuva/60713|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

